title: SNL Alum Jim Breuer Exposes the 'Pure Evil' of Hollywood's Elites
description: Jim Breuer joins Crowder for a long-form conversation with cigars and drinks. They discuss comedy, cancel culture, SNL, and the reaction to Breuer speaking out about government mandates.
